Name: flow
Version: 0.1.0
License: MIT
Authors: Rizo Isrof <rizo@odis.io>
Homepage: http://github.com/rizo/flow
OASISFormat: 0.4
BuildTools: camlp4o,ocamlbuild
Plugins: META (0.4), DevFiles (0.4)

Synopsis:
    Simple, secure and composable abstraction for efficient stream
    processing in a purely functional fashion.
Description:
    This library implements the iteratees style of data processing.
    Iteratees address the problem of doing incremental, composable I/O without being lazy.

